A man died after he was hit by a train at the Florida Railway Station in Roodepoort, Johannesburg, today, paramedics said.The man was believed to be in his 30s, Netcare 911 spokesperson Athlenda Mathe said.&nbsp;Paramedics tried to resuscitate him after he was struck around 08:00. The details about the incident were still unclear.http://www.news24.com/SouthAfrica/News/man-killed-by-train-in-roodepoort-20161123